word_mean_info__list.difference: 指有特定目的远征或探险。
指在水上旅行，尤指海上旅行，也可指空中旅行。
最普通用词，侧重指时间较长、距离较远的单程陆上旅行，也指水上或空中的旅行。
普通用词，口语多用，常指为公务或游玩作的较短暂的旅行。
泛指旅行的行为而不指某次具体的旅行，多指到远方作长期旅行，不强调直接目的地，单、复数均可用。
较正式用词，常指不超过一天的短时期娱乐性游玩，也可指乘火车或轮船往返特定景点的远足旅游。
指最后反回出发地，旅途中有停留游览点，距离可长可短，目的各异的周游或巡行。
主要指乘船的游览并在多处停靠。

bilingual.target: 还有哪些工作涉及旅行？

bilingual.source: They travel a lot for their work.
bilingual.target: 他们因为工作经常旅行。

bilingual.source: Will we find new ways to travel?
bilingual.target: 我们会找到新的旅行方式吗？

bilingual.source: It was a book about space travel.
bilingual.target: 那是一本关于太空旅行的书。

bilingual.source: You don't have to travel to get to work.
I have to travel in a boat for my job.
bilingual.target: 我的工作需要坐船旅行。

bilingual.source: Why is travel so difficult in winter?
bilingual.target: 为什么冬天旅行这么困难？

list.abstract: travel是一个英语单词，有旅行，传送，通过的含义。
Travel，LSB战队教练。 2021年6月1日，LSB公布2021LCK夏季赛大名单，Travel担任教练。

yingyinNormal.en: And how is it you have means to travel?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么有钱旅行?

yingyinNormal.en: No! We've done our ocean travels. That part of our lives is over. The only reason to travel in the first place is so you don't have to travel ever again. Yeah, but I want to...
yingyinNormal.zh: 不!我们不做海洋旅行了.那种日子结束了.旅行唯一的理由就是——以后再也不必旅行了。对，但我想……

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah, sure, let me just put this in a travel mug.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，当然，等我把咖啡倒旅行杯里。

yingyinNormal.en: Our butler takes care of me at home, but when I travel I usually fend for myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在家男管家会照顾我，但我旅行时就得自己打点了。

yingyinNormal.en: Ladies and gentlemen, I have achieved time travel. Thank you. I am farkle!
yingyinNormal.zh: 女士们先生们，这是场时光旅行，谢谢大家，我是法尔科！

yingyinNormal.en: We are what you might call progressive. I hear you're interested in space travel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以称我们是进取者，我听说你对太空旅行很感兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: But the warping of space-time may also provide shortcuts that could make interstellar travel a snap.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但时空的弯曲也许也提供了可以使星际旅行瞬间实现的捷径。

yingyinNormal.en: Mostly, men stay in their village far from the dark of the Jungle. But sometimes they travel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人类生活的村子里，他们远离森林的黑暗，但有些时候他们会旅行。

yingyinNormal.en: Air travel, more than any other mode of modern transportation, has bridged our continent and sped up our lives. And every year, more and more of us are taking to the skies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 航空旅行，对比其他任何现代交通模式，让我们在大陆间更快捷的穿梭每年，我们都有更多的人 选择空中旅行。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't travel with you. I don't keep you warm at night. I don't see you the way he sees you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能和你一起旅行，不能在夜里让你感到温暖，也不能像他那样看待你。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes! You know, in six months, the statute of limitations runs out and I can travel internationally again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然了！再过6个月我的禁令就过期了。到时候我又可以作国际旅行了。

yingyinNormal.en: And for nearly 100 years, America's railways were the fastest and most popular way to travel, but not anymore.
yingyinNormal.zh: 将近100年来，美国的铁路都是最快最流行的旅行方式，不过再也不是了。

yingyinNormal.en: They have another 10 months on their trip home. Space travel is dangerous, they need to be alert and undistracted.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们还有10个月的航程回家，太空旅行很危险，他们需要警觉且不能分心。

yingyinNormal.en: I loved travel, but there're something I really miss when I'm away. What, Daddy? My darlings, of course.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然我热爱旅行，但在我离家的日子里很想念一样东西。什么东西？当然是我亲爱的家人了！

yingyinNormal.en: Space travel has been a staple of the movies from the very beginning, but the feature film Interstellar has a unique pedigree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从最开始，太空旅行就成为电影的主题但故事片《星际穿越》有独特的背景。

yingyinNormal.en: I love to travel. But that something I really miss when I'm away. What, Daddy? My darlings, of course.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哎，虽然我热爱旅行。但在我离家的日子里很想念一样东西。什么东西？当然是我亲爱的家人了！哈哈哈。

yingyinNormal.en: Air travel is so common today that our airways are filled with all kinds of travelers , some of them more unusual than others.
yingyinNormal.zh: 空中旅行变得如此普通了，我们的航空路线到处都是旅行者，其中有那么一些不寻常的。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't we all just settle down for a minute. Look, it's gotten late. Too late to travel. So, why don't we all just have a little honey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在天都晚了，大家先静一静。看，天色已晚，旅行没戏了，要不咱们来点蜂蜜尝尝。

yingyinNormal.en: The chronosphere. The source that powers the grand clock of all time. Legend has, it also lets one travel across the ocean of time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 超时空魔球，据说它就是驱动世界上所有时间的动力源泉，传说通过它还能穿越古今，回到过去，进行时间旅行。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: New travel measures are now directing all travelers from the three affected countries in West Africa into five U.S. airports where we're conducting additional screening.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新的旅行措施正在指引着所有来自西非三个疫区国家的旅客从美国的五个机场入关，在这五个机场我们正在实施着额外的筛查措施。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Travel</highlight> on a London bus and you'll quickly see how this works with drivers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 乘坐伦敦公共汽车旅行，你会很快就会理解它是如何配合司机工作的。

examination_example.sentence: Suppose you have to cancel your <highlight>travel</highlight> plan and will not be able to visit Professor Smith.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假设你不得不取消旅行计划，不能去拜访史密斯教授。

examination_example.sentence: This is the well-travelled road effect: People tend to underestimate the time it takes to <highlight>travel</highlight> a familiar route.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是所谓的“熟路效应”：人们往往会低估在熟悉的线路上旅行所花费的时间。

word_usage.usage:
表示“旅行”
travel泛指旅行的行为而非某次具体的旅行，不强调直接目的地。
trip常指短途往返的旅行，强调目的地或出行原因。
journey主要指时间较长/距离较远的单程陆上旅行，有时也指水上或空中的旅行。
tour指最后会返回出发地的旅行，途中走访不同的地点，距离可长可短。

意为“旅行”，指陆地上的旅行。
意为“旅行”，指水上旅行、航行。
意为“旅行”，指结伴或团体短途旅行。

examination_example.sentence: In fact, so much <highlight>traveling</highlight> was really a good thing because it made us close.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实上，这么多的旅行真的是一件好事，因为它让我们更加亲密。

examination_example.sentence: Nowadays many people <highlight>travel</highlight> across China by means of high-speed trains.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在许多人乘高铁在中国旅行。

examination_example.sentence: They <highlight>travelled</highlight> over snow-covered mountains and sailed hundreds of miles up icy rivers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们在白雪皑皑的群山上旅行，沿着结冰的河流航行数百英里。

examination_example.sentence: It was not widely accepted as a <highlight>travel</highlight> concept until the late 1980s.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 直到20世纪80年代末，它才被广泛接受为一个旅游概念。

examination_example.sentence: As the author explains, this is neither a <highlight>travel</highlight> nor a history book, or even a piece of reportage.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 正如作者所解释的，这既不是一本游记，也不是一本历史书，甚至不是一篇报告文学。

examination_example.sentence: Recently, we bought a twenty-eight-foot <highlight>travel</highlight> trailer complete with a bathroom and a built-in TV set.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近，我们买了一辆28英尺长的旅行拖车，配有浴室和内置电视机。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 最普通用词，侧重指时间较长、距离较远的单程陆上旅行，也指水上或空中的旅行。
指最后反回出发地，旅途中有停留游览点，距离可长可短，目的各异的周游或巡行。
泛指旅行的行为而不指某次具体的旅行，多指到远方作长期旅行，不强调直接目的地，单、复数均可用。
普通用词，口语多用，常指为公务或游玩作的较短暂的旅行。
